Package dev.syndesi.colorconverter.parser.file

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileParser
    Generic class for converting between internally used color-arrays and standardized file-formats.
    FormatAdobeASE
    Class for converting between the internally used color-array and the .ase-fileformat used by Adobe.
    FormatGimp
    Class for converting between the internally used color-array and the .gpl-fileformat used by Gimp and many other applications.
    FormatLibreOffice
    Class for converting between the internally used color-array and the .soc-fileformat used by Libre Office.
